Package com.foreach.across.modules.entity.bind

Class EntityPropertyControlName.ForProperty

java.lang.Object
com.foreach.across.modules.entity.bind.EntityPropertyControlName
com.foreach.across.modules.entity.bind.EntityPropertyControlName.ForProperty
Direct Known Subclasses:
EntityPropertyControlName.ForProperty.CollectionItem, EntityPropertyControlName.ForProperty.MapEntry, EntityPropertyControlName.ForProperty.SingleValue
Enclosing class:
EntityPropertyControlName
public abstract static class EntityPropertyControlName.ForProperty extends EntityPropertyControlName
Represents a general property termination endpoint, usually represented by its direct path. Calling toString() will usually yield the direct property path. Eg. the property named user will have a direct path of user.

Separate methods can be used to convert the current endpoint to a different base type.

    • forHandlingType

      public EntityPropertyControlName forHandlingType(@NonNull @NonNull EntityPropertyHandlingType handlingType)
      Return the current control name adjusted for the property handling type.
      • In case of EntityPropertyHandlingType.MANUAL, a EntityPropertyControlName.ForProperty.SingleValue with the property path will be returned.
      • In case of EntityPropertyHandlingType.BINDER, a EntityPropertyControlName.ForProperty.BinderProperty will be returned
      • In case of EntityPropertyHandlingType.DIRECT, the current control name will be returned
      Returns:
      possibly adjusted control name

    • asSingleValue
